all you'd need is something like

  #if __BIONIC__ || __GLIBC_PREREQ(2, 16)
  #define HAVE_GETAUXVAL 1
  #include <sys/auxv.h>
  #endif

and then just use HAVE_GETAUXVAL everywhere you currently have __BIONIC__...

